e><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nload唔到圖既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nRe upload</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然個表都有講難入口唔一定等於好睇 <br />\n但我反而想知大家係咪覺得易入口就無深度<br />\n<br />\n印象中PTA 之前無咁低 <br />\nInherent Vice 幫佢拉低哂<br />\n<br />\nSoderberg 算唔算兩登比較少人提既主流荷里活導演？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n算，Soderberg拍嘅所謂商業片其實好唔錯，但真係少人提</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黎緊套 logan lucky <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實Lv 5嗰班已經唔係講深度，係實驗性</blockquote><br />\nLV5落去已經唔係用電影法則同理論去拍，而大家講既所謂「深度」都係建基係現有電影理論</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以我上面想問既就係 <br />\n<br />\n係咪大家覺得accessibility 高，咩人都睇得就等同無深度？ <br />\n<br />\n但如果深度/所謂既意義真係咁重要<br />\n甚至乎大過本身套戲好唔好睇<br />\n會唔會有d 本末倒置？</blockquote><br />\n1.我覺得「深度」定義係樓主講既第2種，因為比較多人用深度去形容呢類戲<br />\n係主流文化下既產物多於一個電影評論準則<br />\n就例如你會用「爽快度」去形容一個主流遊戲<br />\n<br />\n2.套戲好唔好睇係出於欣賞角度<br />\n如果係商業片，咁娛樂性就只係唯一既準則，不論有深度與否<br />\n<br />\n3.所謂電影既意義（Message）係影史討論左幾十年，至少我係Buy班大師講既野，電影必需有意義"},{"pid":"6e43ece81c9cc63578bee54556644d161179fc39","tid":269295,"uid":92065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:50:49.000Z","msg":"My Little Sunshine <br />\nMy Name is Khan<br />\nMoonlight <br />\nManchester by the sea <br />\nInterstellar <br />\nBridge of spies<br />\nDead poet society <br />\n呢啲都幾好睇 我覺得睇完會令自己不斷諗野同埋個心戚住戚住就係好好既電影<br />\n自己覺得最好睇既係 Forrest Gump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53da8066b0a3afb8d1dfbd057177e853f7f1d0e6","tid":269295,"uid":57007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T00:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquo